                                            },
                                            "Text": {
                                                "val": "FY13 efforts will continue to focus on the potential to increase combat capability and effectiveness while reducing operating costs.  Continue to fund and execute via the Services or other organizations the efforts started in FY 12 that also require FY 13 funding.  Begin new efforts to improve the operational energy performance of the total force as informed by the gap assessments conducted in FY 12."
